# No Builds — Use Linter for Verification

Do NOT run `go build`, `npm run build`, `cargo build`, `mvn package`, or any other full project build to verify code changes.

The user keeps a dev build running and rebuilds manually. Triggering a build wastes time and is disruptive.

**Instead:** use `ReadLints` (the linter tool) to check for errors after edits.
